docs {
  # Get Task Stats
  
  Get aggregated statistics about tasks.
  
  ## Response
  Returns statistics including:
  - Total task count
  - Counts by status (pending, running, completed, failed, etc.)
  - Counts by task type
  - Average duration
  - Success rate
}

